{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan an Nasai","section":{"1":"The Book of Purification"},"section_detail":{"1":{"hadithnumber_first":1,"hadithnumber_last":324,"arabicnumber_first":1,"arabicnumber_last":324}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":54,"arabicnumber":54,"text":"Rapporté par Anas bin Malik : Un bédouin a uriné dans la mosquée, et le Prophète (ﷺ) a ordonné qu'on apporte un seau et qu'on le verse dessus","grades":[{"name":"Abu Ghuddah","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih - Agreed Upon"}],"reference":{"book":1,"hadith":54}}]}